Installation:

Install a plugin by dropping it in lib/builder_plugins in cruisecontrol.rb


coverage_monitor.rb:
A plugin for Cruisecontrol.rb to export a summery of changes to codecoverage.


statistican.rb:
A plugin to generate a simple graph from rake stats

Requirements:
gnuplot command line utility (http://www.gnuplot.info/)

  sudo port install gnuplot

or

  sudo apt-get install gnuplot

and gnuplot gem

  sudo gem install gnuplot
